					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Sorry, kinda zonked out when I got home.
<br />
<br />kyuusaku is correct, re: Fast/SlowROM times.  "Normal speed" (e.g. "SlowROM") has to be 200ns or faster.  "High speed" (e.g. "FastROM") has to be 120ns or faster.
<br />
<br />This is defined in the manual, section "Super NES Software Submission Requirements", chapter 1.  Revision C, dated 1992/11/02.</div>

